			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">How Terrestrial Turds Lead to Marine Maladies</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Diseases from land animals are killing marine mammals at an alarming rate. Can we stem the flow of feces?</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/jeremy-miller/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Jeremy Miller</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
